•	10:00 AM – 12:00 PM: Meeting with city officials about permits for clients (routine lobbying).
•	12:30 PM – 1:30 PM: Quick lunch; occasionally meets with architects or developers.
•	2:00 PM – 4:00 PM: Calls and emails for personal real estate projects; checking financials and loan statuses.
